      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, known for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox with a precise shift gate and a factory M-Variable differential lock for superior lateral traction. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit overhaul and reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension geometry is maintained via fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, providing the communicative feedback expected of this chassis. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic evidence of a life well-driven, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and compression across all cylinders\u2014remain within tight factory tolerances. Ready for the track or the canyon road.",
      "price": 32500.0,
