    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment. The premium leather seats remain supple; while the driver\u2019s bolster shows light creasing, there are no tears or thinning. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has a comprehensive service history, including a recent oil change and a cooling system flush. The engine pulls smoothly with no hesitation, and the transmission shifts are crisp and predictable. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced last season. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next owner to drive away with total confidence. Clean title in hand.",
